 * - Listbox: `role="listbox"`, `aria-label`.
 * - Options: `role="option"`, `aria-selected`, `aria-disabled`.
 * - Keyboard: ArrowUp/Down navigate options; Enter/Space selects; Escape closes;
 *   Home/End jump to first/last; Tab closes.
